ified application of 1D Fourier series analysis. Although the peak\nstructure at the angular origin is strongly modified in more-central collisions\nsome properties remain compatible with relevant pQCD theory expectations for\njet production.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 23 Jun 2012 19:06:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
